[More about the Centre for AI Fundamentals](https://www.ai-fun.manchester.ac.uk)

I described [Manchester Centre for AI
Fundamentals](https://www.ai-fun.manchester.ac.uk) in a joint meeting
with [Manchester Centre for Robotics and
AI](https://www.robotics.manchester.ac.uk), to kick-start
collaborations. I brought up our mission to develop Fundamentals of
Applied AI, and strong international network [ELLIS](https://ellis.eu)

